Package com.easydataservices.open.auth

Provides the API for persisting and retrieving sessions and attributes that are stored in an AUTH Service repository, hosted by a DB2 for LUW database.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthAttributesDao
    DAO methods for session attributes.
    AuthControlDao
    DAO methods for session control.
    AuthSessionDao
    DAO methods for session retrieval by application.
    SessionConfig
    SessionConfig object, for passing attributes for the CONTROL.SESSION_CONFIG row type.
    StoreAttribute
    StoreAttribute object, representing a persisted session attribute.
    StoreSession
    StoreSession object, representing a persisted session.

Package com.easydataservices.open.auth Description
